						<div class="postbody">It's a cool technique, but though ROM is expensive, its cost per cartridge had dropped from 1983-now.  Scarcity of CPU time on the Fami/NES, however, has remained constant (and higher).  Don't bang your head against the wall doing this -- unless you enjoy the sensation, that is.</div>

					
